9]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tendoku Tennō|ja|崇徳天皇|12=draft}}, the 75th Emperor of Japan (died [[1164]]). * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|宝暦|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1754]] {{ill|July 18|ja|7月18日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kuroda Harutaka|ja|黒田治高|12=draft}}, the 8th lord of the Fukuoka Domain (died [[1782]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1834]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Katsura Hisatake|ja|桂久武|12=draft}}, a politician (died [[1877]]). * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1847]] {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Monoatsukami Takami|ja|物集高見|12=draft}}, a scholar of national literature (died [[1928]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1850]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|12=draft}}) – The first generation of the rakugo performer {{ill|Sanyūtei En'yū|ja|三遊亭圓遊|12=draft}}, a famed storyteller (died [[1907]]).
