{{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 28''' is the 28th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Kenkyū|ja|建久|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1193]] {{ill|June 28|ja|6月28日|qq=}}) – The brothers {{ill|Soga Yūsēi|ja|曾我祐成|qq=}} and {{ill|Soga Tokitomi|ja|曾我時致|qq=}} avenged their father, {{ill|Kawazu Yūtai|ja|河津祐泰|qq=}}, by killing their enemy, {{ill|Kudō Yūkine|ja|工藤祐経|qq=}}, during the conflict known as {{ill|Genkō no Ran|ja|元弘の乱|qq=}}.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-04|qq=}}</ref> * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 1|ja|6月1日|qq=}}) – The shogun, {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=}}, mobilized his forces to confront the situation during the summer siege of Osaka. * {{ill|Tenmei|ja|天保|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1786]] {{ill|June 1|ja|6月1日|qq=}}) – Under orders from the Tokugawa shogunate, the commander {{ill|Saigō Tokunai|ja|最上徳内|qq=}} landed on 【Oki Province】 (隠岐) to secure the area. == Births == * {{ill|Gen'ei|ja|元永|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1119]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tendoku Tennō|ja|崇徳天皇|qq=}}, the 75th Emperor of Japan (died [[1164]]). * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|宝暦|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1754]] {{ill|July 18|ja|7月18日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kuroda Harutaka|ja|黒田治高|qq=}}, the 8th lord of the Fukuoka Domain (died [[1782]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1834]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Katsura Hisatake|ja|桂久武|qq=}}, a politician (died [[1877]]). * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1847]] {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Monoatsukami Takami|ja|物集高見|qq=}}, a scholar of national literature (died [[1928]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1850]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=}}) – The first generation of the rakugo performer {{ill|Sanyūtei En'yū|ja|三遊亭圓遊|qq=}}, a famed storyteller (died [[1907]]).
