* [[Keichō]] 20th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Katagiri Kagetora|ja|片桐且元|qq=|12=draft}}, a daimyō (born [[1556]]).

