_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1119]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Tendoku Tennō|ja|崇徳天皇|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 75th Emperor of Japan (died [[1164]]). * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|宝暦|qq=|qq=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1754]] {{ill|July 18|ja|7月18日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Kuroda Harutaka|ja|黒田治高|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 8th lord of the Fukuoka Domain (died [[1782]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1834]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Katsura Hisatake|ja|桂久武|qq=|qq=draft}}, a politician (died [[1877]]). * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1847]] {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Monoatsukami Takami|ja|物集高見|qq=|qq=draft}}, a scholar of national literature (died [[1928]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1850]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – The first generation of the rakugo performer {{ill|Sanyūtei En'yū|ja|三遊亭圓遊|qq=|qq=draft}}, a famed storyteller (died [[1907]]).
== Deaths == * [[Gangyō]] 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[880]] {{ill|July 9|ja|7月9日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Ariwara no Narihira|ja|在原業平|qq=|qq=draft}}, a renowned waka poet and one of the Six Immortals of Poetry (born [[825]]). * {{ill|Kenkyū|ja|建久|qq=|qq=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1193]] {{ill|June 28|ja|6月28日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Soga Yūsēi|ja|曾我祐成|qq=|qq=draft}}, a samurai and elder brother among the Soga brothers (born [[1172]]). * [[Keichō]] 20th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Katagiri Kagetora|ja|片桐且元|qq=|qq=draft}}, a daimyō (born [[1556]]).
