|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1786]] {{ill|June 1|ja|6月1日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 1|qq=}}) – Under orders from the Tokugawa shogunate, the commander {{ill|Saigō Tokunai|ja|最上徳内|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saigō Tokunai|qq=}} landed on 【Oki Province】 (隠岐) to secure the area. == Births == * {{ill|Gen'ei|ja|元永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gen'ei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1119]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 7|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tendoku Tennō|ja|崇徳天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tendoku Tennō|qq=}}, the 75th Emperor of Japan (died [[1164]]). * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|宝暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōreki|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1754]] {{ill|July 18|ja|7月18日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 18|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kuroda Harutaka|ja|黒田治高|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroda Harutaka|qq=}}, the 8th lord of the Fukuoka Domain (died [[1782]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1834]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 4|qq=}}) – {{ill|Katsura Hisatake|ja|桂久武|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Katsura Hisatake|qq=}}, a politician (died [[1877]]). * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōka|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1847]] {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 10|qq=}}) – {{ill|Monoatsukami Takami|ja|物集高見|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Monoatsukami Takami|qq=}}, a scholar of national literature (died [[1928]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1850]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 7|qq=}}) – The first generation of the rakugo performer {{ill|Sanyūtei En'yū|ja|三遊亭圓遊|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sanyūtei En'yū|qq=}}, a famed storyteller (died [[1907]]).
== Deaths == * [[Gangyō]] 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[880]] {{ill|July 9|ja|7月9日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 9|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ariwara no Narihira|ja|在原業平|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ariwara no Narihira|qq=}}, a renowned waka poet and one of the Six Immortals of Poetry (born [[825]]). * {{ill|Kenkyū|ja|建久|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenkyū|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1193]] {{ill|June 28|ja|6月28日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 28|qq=}}) – {{ill|Soga Yūsēi|ja|曾我祐成|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga Yūsēi|qq=}}, a samurai and elder brother among the Soga brothers (born [[1172]]). * [[Keichō]] 20th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 24|qq=}}) – {{ill|Katagiri Kagetora|ja|片桐且元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Katagiri Kagetora|qq=}}, a daimyō (born [[1556]]).
