== Events == * {{ill|Kenkyū|ja|建久|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenkyū|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1193]] {{ill|June 28|ja|6月28日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 28|qq=}}) – The brothers {{ill|Soga Yūsēi|ja|曾我祐成|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga Yūsēi|qq=}} and {{ill|Soga Tokitomi|ja|曾我時致|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga Tokitomi|qq=}} avenged their father, {{ill|Kawazu Yūtai|ja|河津祐泰|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kawazu Yūtai|qq=}}, by killing their enemy, {{ill|Kudō Yūkine|ja|工藤祐経|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kudō Yūkine|qq=}}, during the conflict known as {{ill|Genkō no Ran|ja|元弘の乱|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkō no Ran|qq=}}.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-04|qq=}}</ref> * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genna|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 1|ja|6月1日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 1|qq=}}) – The shogun, {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}}, mobilized his forces to confront the situation during the summer siege of Osaka. * {{ill|Tenmei|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmei|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦